Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please listen to today's confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prietena mea e un Lord Demon care se enervează mereu din nimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surioară!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acum că ai declarat război celor Șapte Păcate Mortale, cred că ar trebui să te gândești la o poziție de victorie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu fi proastă!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deja mi-am ales-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce părere ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uimitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arată-mi mai mult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce spui de asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ești cea mai tare, surioară!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acum încearcă una sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acum una provocatoare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adică... așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu e îndeajuns pentru clienți!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Una mai provocatoare!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put some effort into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bună treabă, Lucifer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acum, haide să începem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te rog, nu face asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Au!
